{"tid":2229351,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"男性朋友真係好小氣又無風度","createTime":"2020-10-04T10:25:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T02:30:49.000Z","uid":324904,"like":3,"dislike":62,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"aac5b83724f819769d8e25c817e1937ffec21f62","tid":2229351,"uid":324904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T10:25:55.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n<br />\n我識左呢個男仔都一排，但法國佢真係好小氣！<br />\n<br />\n本身初頭都好正面，通常我話有野想買咪約佢出街，點知佢買定比我，我已經覺得奇怪！不過佢送比我我梗係要啦，同埋食飯佢地會主動比錢，本來都覺得幾有風度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n見佢個人幾好咁分享下我興趣比佢知，咁食飯咪介紹下我鋼琴老師佢識，我老師又靚仔又型，把聲又好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知佢話約我出街唔想知其他男仔既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家評下理啦，有乜理由咁小氣先得架你話<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n重有就係成日係whatsapp chur住我，我好忙架，都盡量隔3/4日就應下佢架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n近期我想買個Lv，見佢出開尖沙咀咪想佢幫我望下，咁都唔肯，小家到呢⋯⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n早兩日重無啦啦話咩唔再做兵，話我係搵佢攝時間、等佢送野<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n喂，佢自願送野比我，我又無迫佢，我另一個朋友話送相機或iphone比我都係咁啦<br />\n<br />\n我明明都無收兵，玻璃心到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家啲男人真係好小氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbf9a51f69acddcf83357613a47a41f4ce283b61","tid":2229351,"uid":68081,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T10:28:04.000Z","msg":"樓主來自波台是常識吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\